    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six breathes through individual throttle bodies, providing exceptional throttle response and a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise throws, sending power to the rear wheels through a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including Vanos adjustment and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with spirited use, the suspension kinematics remain tight, and the hydraulic steering rack provides the unfiltered feedback enthusiasts demand. A driver-spec icon ready for the apex.",
